<c0><fC>Keyboard Settings<c1><i2>You can select which keys should activate what functions in this dialog.  Click in one of the small rectangles which shows the current key settings.  The rectangle will be outlined in light blue. Then simply hit the key you want to assign to this function.   You can go to the next key by hitting tab.  If you assign the same key to multiple functions, this fact will be highlighted at the bottom of the screen.<c0><fC>Joystick Settings<c1><i2>If you have a gamepad or joystick you would like to use. Plug it in before you run the game. Device customization can be done via the devices screen in the settings tab.